From 25946d7cce0d812bddec2ea3142a96d7c9f020d3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Victor Kipruto <victor@shuleni.co.ke>
Date: Wed, 17 Jun 2026 07:27:20 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Complete music app: fix login/logout bugs, add Song model,
 routes, and full player UI

- Fix: login endpoint now returns JWT token after successful auth
- Fix: Header logout now correctly uses this.$store.dispatch (was this.route.dispatch)
- Add: Song model (title, artist, album, url, coverUrl, duration)
- Add: SongController with index, create, show, destroy
- Add: Song API routes (GET/POST /songs, GET/DELETE /songs/:id)
- Add: SongService.js for frontend API calls
- Complete: Songs.vue now has full music player UI with play/pause,
  next/prev, seek bar, volume control, cover art, and add/delete forms
- Update: README with full documentation, setup instructions, and bug fix log
